            "body": "<p>You can add your vars to a list and use simply the sort method from java.util.Collections which will do the comparing for you. Example<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public static void main(String var1, String var2){ \n\n    List&lt;String&gt; varList = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();\n    varList.add(var1); \n    varList.add(var2); \n\n    java.util.Collections.sort(varList);\n    System.out.println(\"designation of newer version is: \" + varList.get(1));\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
